This topic describes cloud properties for different resources created by the SoftLayer CPI.

## <a id='azs'></a> AZs

Currently SoftLayer CPI does not support any cloud properties for AZs.

Example:

```yaml
azs:
- name: z1
```

---
## <a id='networks'></a> Networks


Currently SoftLayer CPI does not support any cloud properties for Networks.

Example of dynamic network:

```yaml
networks:
- name: default
  type: dynamic
  dns: 
  - 8.8.8.8
```

Currently SoftLayer CPI does not support manual or vip networks.

